Conditional Statements:-


    Ternary Operator are used to perform one line if else condition.

    Switch Statements 

Loops in java:

    for
    while 
    do while 
    Nested loops 

    loop(){
        loop(){}
    }

    for loop as while loop :-

    int  i=23; // intisilised 

    for(;i>34;){
        i++
    }

